  <brief_title>Olmesartan as an Add-on to Amlodipine in Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Add-on Study of Olmesartan Medoxomil in Patients With Moderate to Severe Hypertension Not Achieving Target Blood Pressure on Amlodipine 5 mg Alone</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Sankyo Pharma Gmbh</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Daiichi Sankyo, Inc.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to test the efficacy and safety of the combination of olmesartan and amlodipine
      in hypertensive patients whose blood pressure is not adequately controlled with amlodipine
      alone
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
